WEBVTT

00:00:01.520 --> 00:00:37.409
Rabbi, who sinned?

00:00:37.409 --> 00:00:42.219
This man or his parents so that he was born blind?

00:00:42.219 --> 00:00:46.619
Needed this man sinned nor his parents.

00:00:46.619 --> 00:00:59.859
But it was so that the works of God might be made manifest in his case.

00:00:59.859 --> 00:01:19.420
As long as I am in the world, I am the world's light.

00:01:19.420 --> 00:01:20.939
Go wash in the pool of Salon.
